{"tid":1615894,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"是咁的，下個月其中一條主線","createTime":"2019-10-03T08:37:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-26T05:24:34.000Z","uid":81591,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"44b225db816feed0330d532761f5a3640e8f41f5","tid":1615894,"uid":81591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T08:37:59.000Z","msg":"大家好，我地係自由系，一班為區選戰線出錢出力既傻仔，有抗爭既時候會係大家既後援，無抗爭既時候會係大家落地既文宣告示版。我地依班傻仔一直抱住個心態就係對抗建制，希望成為大家十一月既區選戰線既同路人，係制度內外同政府表達我地既訴求。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">係煲底外，你係我地既前線。<br />\n係制度內，我成為你既前線。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我地由六月中開始成立，一直維持住區選既戰線，平時為左唔好分散大家既注意力，都唔敢搞太多動作。由六月起，我地開始由各區招募白區義士，同各大小黨派，本土組織協調，希望可以為非建制候選人得到一個最大勝算既局面。另一方面，自由系亦透過唔同平台搵人幫手安排素人需要既training，提供法律及選舉知識既支援，以不被捕為大前提。亦有d痴線既巴打，幫手安排影相同拍理念片，搞fb page，減輕宣傳既壓力。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J9Bomax.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ9Bomax.jpg&h=491ca5e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">你可能會問，佢地星期六日個陣去左邊？</span></span><br />\n大家都會盡力於有限的時間內 做最多的工作 務求於制度內 成功入閘 只有入到閘至可以起到最低限度既作用 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">你可能會問，自由系係咪搞大台？</span></span><br />\n大就唔敢認，其實我地係一個平台，依個平台咩立場都無，得一個目標，就係打倒建制，希望做到資源運用，唔夠人就可以透過平台去搵人幫手。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">點樣證明素人唔係鬼？</span></span><br />\n無架，真係證明唔曬，我地每區都有個admin 負責聯絡同區素人，有d區係大家投選出黎，有d區係核心圈子見完ok再由大家去幫手。到底admin 同素人係咪有建制既背景我地都唔完全清楚，要靠大家幫手去加入素人團隊，了解清楚佢地既背景。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jVMr3oX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjVMr3oX.jpg&h=2c64cbd7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">加入方式</span></span><br />\nTG 區議會公海: （請各位先加入公海，入面會有各區admin 及 自由系核心團隊 tg 名單）<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/DistrictCouncil2019\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FDistrictCouncil2019&d=2%2FeNT3TbtuwIHwt2a%2FmQGGCvuqnjOb%2FiGpmC2gL%2Fng4%3D&h=8fc00a6a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/DistrictCouncil2019</a><br />\n自由系 FB page: <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">（大家請盡可能like／share）</span></strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hkhifreedom/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhkhifreedom%2F&d=2%2FeNT3TbtuwIHwt2a%2FmQGGCvuqnjOb%2FiGpmC2gL%2Fng4%3D&h=a8c83fc1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hkhifreedom/</a><br />\n自由系 IG:<br />\nHkhifreedom"},{"pid":"bdaa0bfd60d802756340c8f9d9403965aee8af86","tid":1615894,"uid":2526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T08:48:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"03b8f5fb8f6f6c69633fcc428c49c07f930de187","tid":1615894,"uid":2526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T08:49:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8be87e9c674467488220ee462fa2d623c76c23b6","tid":1615894,"uid":2526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T08:50:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4f38606e562ab9a52fcf852c1eab3ed8c9f32486","tid":1615894,"uid":2526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T08:50:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d104f366aba771dec864306cba7705b172cea9cc","tid":1615894,"uid":2526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T08:50:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4019c183f9a710872ce7e58e78f7cde5292fb410","tid":1615894,"uid":2526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T08:51:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a32285d93b3a518a35963a88b502309a24fc492f","tid":1615894,"uid":2526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T08:51:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f34a6d84891abe537c290b1b6f0548a846a20979","tid":1615894,"uid":2526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T08:52:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"166ff2041